snippet: It’s not just around the greens that Tiger Woods has looked heavy-handed. His reaction to a book by his former swing coach has been needlessly contentious.
abstract: Karen Crouse On Golf column on Tiger Woods, who is tied for 68th after first round of Honda Classic golf tournament; notes Woods's reaction to tell-all book by his former swing coach Hank Haney.
lead_paragraph: It’s not just around the greens that Tiger Woods has looked heavy-handed. His reaction to a book by his former swing coach has been needlessly contentious.

headline.seo: Humbled, but Still Short of Humility
